00:03:54.615 --> 00:03:59.292
Let's start by understanding
what digital accessibility is.

00:03:59.981 --> 00:04:01.658
Accessibility means

00:04:01.679 --> 00:04:08.194
creating a digital content, website,
applications, document, tools, systems,

00:04:08.234 --> 00:04:11.197
usable and understandable by everyone,

00:04:11.217 --> 00:04:13.752
including people with disability.

00:04:14.294 --> 00:04:18.408
Creating a document
or creating a digital content accessible

00:04:18.428 --> 00:04:22.862
need to make sure that
it is going to be inclusive

00:04:22.882 --> 00:04:25.861
and usable by everyone.

00:04:27.339 --> 00:04:30.955
Making a content digital
does not limit only

00:04:30.975 --> 00:04:34.749
by focusing on people
with permanent disability,

00:04:34.809 --> 00:04:38.531
but it should also help people
with situational disability.

00:04:38.561 --> 00:04:41.909
It should enhance
the overall user experience.

00:04:42.249 --> 00:04:43.920
For instance,

00:04:44.505 --> 00:04:49.911
we would have seen people
using a dark mode on their devices.

00:04:50.084 --> 00:04:54.813
Sometimes it is about preference,
but sometimes it is about need.

00:04:55.125 --> 00:04:59.237
For example,
people using a device in a dark mode

00:04:59.257 --> 00:05:02.696
wherein they are
in a low-light condition.

00:05:03.073 --> 00:05:05.991
Now, a dark mode becomes a necessity.

00:05:06.076 --> 00:05:11.362
It helps in reducing the eye strain,
and it also help by providing

00:05:11.473 --> 00:05:15.294
a good readable view for the user.

00:05:15.733 --> 00:05:19.589
To take another example,
we might have experienced a situation

00:05:19.609 --> 00:05:22.474
wherein we have to complete a task

00:05:22.494 --> 00:05:29.352
or maybe call an urgent person
for some reason,

00:05:30.699 --> 00:05:36.173
and in this situation, we would not have
our glasses handy with us.

00:05:36.398 --> 00:05:37.585
In this situation,

00:05:37.633 --> 00:05:43.142
features like text-to-speech
or a screen magnifier comes handy.

00:05:43.186 --> 00:05:48.250
It helps us in completing the task
and making that urgent phone call.

00:05:48.968 --> 00:05:51.186
Now, the next question is why?

00:05:51.220 --> 00:05:54.931
Why create all digital content accessible?

00:05:55.178 --> 00:05:59.178
The main goal for creating
any digital content accessible

00:05:59.198 --> 00:06:02.134
is to make sure everyone can use it,

00:06:02.154 --> 00:06:05.535
everyone can interact
with the product,

00:06:05.684 --> 00:06:11.366
and obviously, allowing
everyone to participate equally.

00:06:12.278 --> 00:06:15.936
Also, in some region,
there are legal requirements.

00:06:16.121 --> 00:06:20.868
The digital product
must meet to specifically adhere

00:06:20.888 --> 00:06:23.829
to some accessibility standards.

00:06:25.150 --> 00:06:28.904
Now, apart from legal compliances,

00:06:29.159 --> 00:06:36.098
making a digital content accessible also
comes in place to improve the brand value,

00:06:36.795 --> 00:06:42.273
and it's also provide more values
in terms of business.

00:06:42.522 --> 00:06:43.723
For example,

00:06:43.811 --> 00:06:46.454
it boosts the brand reputation

00:06:46.474 --> 00:06:49.414
by showing it it is inclusive,

00:06:49.434 --> 00:06:52.816
it is based on users' need,

00:06:53.023 --> 00:06:56.674
and also it improves audience reach.

00:06:56.830 --> 00:06:59.403
It creates a customer base.

00:07:00.552 --> 00:07:05.615
Apart from all these benefits,
like enhancing SEOs,

00:07:05.890 --> 00:07:09.047
creating a content accessible

00:07:09.067 --> 00:07:10.783
is the right thing to do

00:07:10.803 --> 00:07:15.480
as it makes sure that
the product is usable by everyone

00:07:15.500 --> 00:07:18.690
in different conditions
or situations.

00:07:21.495 --> 00:07:24.209
Nowadays, we have seen a rise,

00:07:24.229 --> 00:07:29.496
a major rise when it comes to
creating a web page

00:07:29.535 --> 00:07:33.923
or building a website
with the help of AI.

00:07:35.533 --> 00:07:40.226
AI is not limited only
by generating content,

00:07:40.274 --> 00:07:43.787
but nowadays, it's very much in use

00:07:43.807 --> 00:07:47.276
in different stages
of website development.

00:07:48.315 --> 00:07:52.372
It can provide visuals,
like it can create icons,

00:07:52.393 --> 00:07:54.421
it can create images.

00:07:54.494 --> 00:07:59.765
It can provide suggestion
in terms of layouts, color schemes.

00:08:00.099 --> 00:08:03.281
It writes code in HTML and CSS.

00:08:03.524 --> 00:08:05.427
All this can be just done

00:08:05.447 --> 00:08:09.239
with the help of a simple
plain language prompt

00:08:09.260 --> 00:08:11.026
by a user.

00:08:12.222 --> 00:08:17.869
It can also create a full-page content,
and again, just by a simple prompt.

00:08:19.358 --> 00:08:25.009
Such kind of AI tool simplifies
the work of a developer and a designer,

00:08:25.030 --> 00:08:30.724
but with that, it also opens the door
for a non-technical user.

00:08:31.194 --> 00:08:35.709
Now, someone who is not well-versed
with development and designing,

00:08:35.858 --> 00:08:41.415
but can yet create a functional
and a well-structured website.

00:08:43.214 --> 00:08:45.150
Such kind of AI feature

00:08:45.170 --> 00:08:48.610
helps especially small business
and individuals

00:08:48.639 --> 00:08:54.117
who may not have a budget
or a resource to hire a full team.

