and it is easier,

00:10:17.583 --> 00:10:22.447
and it is more adaptable
when it comes to dynamic changes.

00:10:23.158 --> 00:10:27.576
AI especially helps people
who often struggle on understanding

00:10:27.596 --> 00:10:31.279
where to start in terms of content

00:10:31.290 --> 00:10:35.749
or in terms of understanding
the page structure or the layouts.

00:10:36.176 --> 00:10:38.990
AI becomes a starting point.

00:10:39.170 --> 00:10:43.871
AI nowadays has turned
into a built-in guide

00:10:43.891 --> 00:10:47.096
in helping user to start with.

00:10:47.274 --> 00:10:53.455
AI is beneficial when it comes to
including the AI features

00:10:53.475 --> 00:10:57.341
from the very beginning of the product
